data.name: Mercedes-Benz X-Class
data.description:
Great design, stylish and comfortable , this Mercedes Benz X 350D Ute allows you to travel in style or help you transport your tools or items in the tray with ease. 
Having a V6 Turbo Diesel producing 190KW and 550NM of torque , this will get going! Experience this unique luxury UTE by Mercedes Benz.
